                  <msItem rend="visible">
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">באור שמות קדש וחול</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Beʼur Shemot ḳodesh ṿe-ḥol</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>On the Torah, until Parashat Shoftim.</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The title within the manuscripts attributes the work to Maimonides (on this see, Samuel Klein, Toldot ha-yishuv ha-Yehudi be-Erets-Yiśraʼel : me-ḥatimat ha-Talmud ʿad tenuʿat "Yishuv E.Y.," Tel-Aviv : "Mitspah" 695 [1935], p. 128). </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>At its end (ff. 50a-52a) is an excerpt from a composition on the grammar and the accents of the Bible, mentioning David Kimhi.</p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                     
                     
                     
                     <filiation>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Published by Moses Gaster in Devir 1 (1922/23): 191-222.</p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </filiation>
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="1v" to="52v"/>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
               
               
               
               </msContents>
               
               
               
